On this week’s episode of Portfolio Watch we examine the impact of the global tech war following US president Donald Trump’s decision to ban Huawei from operating in the US joined by Andre Cilliers, Director at TreasuryONE and Leigh Riley, Wealth Manager at AlphaWealth. In the second half of Portfolio watch we take a look at how many of the heavy weights on the JSE have invited the public to participate in its BBBEE schemes, and how you can create profits for your portfolio joined by Riaz Gardee, BEE Commentator and Craig Gradidge, Investment & Retirement Planning Specialist, GM investments.

